title: Maverick 218 The Rivals [retr?tv]
description:
MAVERICK 218 The Rivals   1/25/1959 *REPOST*

An English millionaire, Jack Vandergelt III, exchanges identities with Bret Maverick hoping to win the affections of a young lady who can&#039;t stand wealthy men. On the other hand, Bret needs the high society name to get into the swanky casino hotel.
					
This season 2 episode features Roger Moore playing a non-Maverick character in a sophisticated drawing room comedy based on a play by Richard Brinsley Sheridan originally produced in 1775. Moore would later be a regular series lead as Beau Maverick in season 4. 

Stars: James Garner (Bret Maverick), Jack Kelly (Bart Maverick)
Guest stars: Roger Moore (Jack Vandergelt III), Dan Tobin (Lucious Benson), Patricia Crowley (Lydia Lynley), Barbara Jo Allen (Mrs. Malaver), Neil Hamilton (Brigadier Archibald Vandergelt)], Sandra Gould (Lucy Marshall), William Allyn (Livingston), Chet Stratton (Desk Clerk)
